## Task A: Add methods to `internal/account/convex.go`

File: `/Users/rejoesudarsan/Projects/nurgesh/internal/account/convex.go`

This file already has `ConvexClient` struct with `baseURL` and `httpClient` fields, plus methods like `ValidateToken`, `ExchangeGoogleToken`, `SendEmail`, `RevokeToken`. It already imports `bytes`, `encoding/json`, `fmt`, `io`, `net/http`, `time`, `errors`.

